title: TEKE::TEKE - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents TEKE::TEKE performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded October 20th, 2023.

Songs:
Setagaya Koya
Gotoku Lemon
Onaji Heya
Hoppe

Sei Nakauchi Pelletier - Guitar
Maya Kuroki - Lead Singer
Hidetaka Yoneyama - Guitar
Mishka Stein - Bass
Ian Lettre - Drums
Yuki Isami - Flutes, Keyboard, Taisho Koto
Etienne Lebel - Trombone

Host: Jewel Loree
Audio Engineers: Jon Roberts
Audio Mixer: Jon Roberts
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Alaia D’Alessandro, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen
Editor: Carlos Cruz
